SUMMARY="OpenStack Image API Client Library & Tools"
DESCRIPTION="
This is a client library for Glance built on the OpenStack Images API.
It provides a Python API (the glanceclient module) and a command-line
tool (glance). This library fully supports the v1 Images API, while
support for the v2 API is in progress.
"
